"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-11-Who-did-CGTN-Sports-Scene-talk-to-during-2024-Paris-Summer-Olympics--1vYVU73uuYw-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Sports Scene  Copied  The 2024 Paris Summer Olympics will end on Sunday evening and so will CGTN Sports Scene's special program \\\"Meet in Paris\\\" as well as its \\\"Talk Sports\\\" series.  A total of 31 athletes and officials participated in interviews for the \\\"Talk Sports\\\" series focusing on the 2024 Games in Paris. Here are some of the highlights.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"